ily:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;">랜덤 댄스에 아동이 좋아하는 곡이 나오자 춤을 따라 추며 즐기는 모습이 귀여웠습니다</span><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-family:굴림;mso-ascii-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;">^^</span></p><p class="0"><span style="font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;">비가 와 좋은 날씨는 아니였지만 박</span><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-family:굴림;mso-ascii-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;">*</span><span style="font-family:굴림;mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;">수 아동이 잘 참여하는 모습이 좋았습니다</span><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-fareast-font-family:굴림;font-family:굴림;mso-ascii-font-family:굴림;mso-font-width:100%;letter-spacing:0pt;mso-text-raise:0pt;">.</span></p>          </td>
        </tr>',828,1729177200,'', '', '', '', '', '');
