<p class="0" style="background: #ffffff; text-align: left; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt"><span style="background: #ffffff; letter-spacing: -0.6pt; font-size: 13pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 휴먼고딕"><span style="background: #ffffff; letter-spacing: -0.6pt; font-size: 13pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 휴먼고딕">안면을 익힐 수 있던 <span style="background: #ffffff; letter-spacing: -0.6pt; font-size: 13pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 휴먼고딕">시간이었다고 합니다</span><span lang="EN-US" style="background: #ffffff; letter-spacing: -0.6pt; font-size: 13pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 휴먼고딕; mso-ascii-font-family: 휴먼고딕; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt">. </span></span></span></p>
<p class="0" style="background: #ffffff; text-align: left; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt"><span style="background: #ffffff; letter-spacing: -0.6pt; font-size: 13pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 휴먼고딕"><span style="background: #ffffff; letter-spacing: -0.6pt; font-size: 13pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 휴먼고딕"><span lang="EN-US" style="background: #ffffff; letter-spacing: -0.6pt; font-size: 13pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 휴먼고딕; mso-ascii-font-family: 휴먼고딕; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt"></span><span style="background: #ffffff; letter-spacing: -0.6pt; font-size: 13pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 휴먼고딕">앞으로의 대학생활 시간도 알차게 보낼 수 있기를 응원합니다</span><span lang="EN-US" style="background: #ffffff; letter-spacing: -0.6pt; font-family: 휴먼고딕; font-size: 13pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 휴먼고딕; mso-ascii-font-family: 휴먼고딕; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt"><font face="굴림">.</font></span></span></span></p>          </td>
