<p class="0" style="letter-spacing: 0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-padding-alt: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-font-width: 100%; mso-text-raise: 0pt"><span style="mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕"><span style="mso-fareast-font-family: 함초롬바탕">아동이 롯테타워에서 즐거운 추억 많이 쌓고 귀원하길 바랍니다.</span></span></p>          </td>
        </tr>',943,1543158000,'', '', '', '', '', '');
